{'story_metadata': {'story_id': 'US-068', 'elaboration_date': '2025-01-24', 'development_readiness': 'Complete'}, 'story_narrative': {'title': "View the game's data privacy statement", 'as_a_user_story': 'As a privacy-conscious user, I want to access and read a clear data privacy statement from the main menu, so that I can understand what data the game collects, how it is stored, and confirm that it operates entirely offline, which builds my trust in the application.', 'user_persona': 'Any user of the game, particularly those concerned with data privacy and application behavior.', 'business_value': "Enhances user trust and transparency by clearly communicating the game's offline nature and local-only data handling. Fulfills standard software best practices and mitigates potential user concerns about data collection.", 'functional_area': 'User Interface - Main Menu', 'story_theme': 'Application Support and Usability'}, 'acceptance_criteria': [{'criteria_id': 'AC-001', 'scenario': 'Accessing the Privacy Statement from the Main Menu', 'scenario_type': 'Happy_Path', 'given': 'the user is on the main menu screen', 'when': "the user clicks the 'Privacy Policy' button", 'then': "a modal view or dedicated screen appears, displaying the game's data privacy statement, and the main menu UI elements become non-interactive."}, {'criteria_id': 'AC-002', 'scenario': 'Closing the Privacy Statement View', 'scenario_type': 'Happy_Path', 'given': 'the privacy statement view is open', 'when': "the user clicks the 'Close' or 'Back' button", 'then': 'the privacy statement view is dismissed, and the main menu UI elements become interactive again.'}, {'criteria_id': 'AC-003', 'scenario': 'Verifying Privacy Statement Content', 'scenario_type': 'Happy_Path', 'given': 'the privacy statement view is open', 'when': 'the user reads the content', 'then': "the text must accurately reflect the statements in SRS section 11.2, explicitly confirming that the application operates entirely offline, all 